                                        alt="Author - Andy Hume"
                                        src="http://sitepointstatic.com/graphics/author_andy_hume.jpg"
                                />
                                Andy lives in London and works as a Web developer at <a class="sublink" href="http://www.multimap.com">Multimap.com</a>, with a focus on Web standards, accessibility, and usability. He writes about Web development, design, and typography at <a class="sublink" href="http://usabletype.com">UsableType.com</a>.
